EDI Document 840 - Request for Quotation
Function:
The EDI 840 Request for Quotation (RFQ) document is used to solicit price and delivery information from suppliers for goods or services.

Example:

ISA*00*          *00*          *ZZ*SENDERID      *ZZ*RECEIVERID    *YYMMDD*HHMM*U*00501*000000001*0*P*>~
GS*RF*SENDERID*RECEIVERID*YYMMDD*HHMM*1*X*005010~
ST*840*0001~
BFR*00*ORIGINAL CONTROL NUMBER*ORIGINAL DATE*ORIGINAL TIME*TRANSACTION TYPE*ORIGINAL REFERENCE NUMBER~
DTM*002*20230701~
N1*SU*BUYER NAME*92*BUYERID~
N1*ST*SUPPLIER NAME*92*SUPPLIERID~
LIN*1*PRODUCT CODE*UPC*PRODUCT DESCRIPTION~
UIT*EA~
PO4*1*100*EA~
DTM*010*20230701~
SE*10*0001~
GE*1*1~
IEA*1*000000001~

Purpose in Lizgate Enterprise:
In Lizgate Enterprise, the EDI 840 document streamlines the procurement process by automating the solicitation of price and delivery information from suppliers, facilitating efficient sourcing decisions and improving supplier relationships.